      "body" : "The drawback is that years/months have very large granularity, ie you cannot see progress in the beginning.\r\nMonths also don't seem to be a good measure of time to me as they vary wildly in length.\r\n\r\nWhat about:\r\n- \"%n week(s)\" if <=1 year\r\n- \"%n year(s) and %n week(s)\" if >1year\r\n",
